abstract: All but one of 29 West Coast seaports begin workweek, with crews loading and unloading cargo ships that had been held up amid a contract dispute.
lead_paragraph: All but one of 29 West Coast seaports began the workweek on Monday with crews loading and unloading cargo ships that had been held up amid a contract dispute.
